            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Thou shalt think an evil thought; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and these mischievous thoughts thou shalt so manage, as to forecast how they may, and to set on the execution till they do, take effect. If Antiochus Epiphanes be this Gag, Daniel, in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
